---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "About im462",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-12">About</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>Hi, I’m im462.</p>
		<p>
			This blog is where I collect posts, notes, and small experiments. I like simple tools, clean
			interfaces, and writing things down before they disappear.
		</p>
		<p>A few things you will probably see here:</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>short notes on things I am learning</li>
			<li>posts about code, tools, and the web</li>
			<li>small experiments worth keeping around</li>
			<li>links to places you can reach me</li>
		</ul>
		<p>
			You can find me on <a
				class="cactus-link inline-block"
				href="https://github.com/white2q"
				rel="noreferrer"
				target="_blank">GitHub</a
			>, or add me on QQ: <strong>2513732602</strong>.
		</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
